First project requires:
Image for the ball.
Functionality to create obstacles greater than 3 pixels with the mouse.
A way to start and close the game (UI for starting menu and a UI for in-game menu).

Second project requires: 
Image(s) for the car.
Image(s) for the obstacles.
A main menu UI, a way to start the game in the UI, and a menu to return to the main menu.
A game over image that appears if the player crashes the car, along with a menu to try again or return to main menu.
